Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:11.57,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy being a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:17.03,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm a monster, no matter how many times that golem punched me, I didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:22.58,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a monster, I'm able to stand up to that golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.88,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I will use my power to protect those I cherish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:31.96,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm fortunate... to be a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:32.89,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.43,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'll let it end this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:35.43,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazaki-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:38.55,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:42.43,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'll let it end... in such a stupid way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.27,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Ellis, I had her go ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:40.99,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I should think she's reached her target by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:45.95,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps... the target might already have been shredded to chunks of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:48.33,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You piece of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.71,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:53.20,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,You just stay here and be my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.92,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately that girl got by.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.04,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:59.51,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared you were able to destroy Ellis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.47,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I want war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.80,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:09.22,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a balance between\Nmagic and science, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:10.46,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:15.83,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,When espers use magic, their body will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.52,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of that at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:19.23,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.90,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you think that was weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.35,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,How would anyone know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:29.32,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Because someone tried to, around twenty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:32.43,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,back when there was a movement to have magic and science walk together,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:34.92,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,which was started by one of our inner factions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:40.05,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,They were trying to give birth to a new type of caster that possessed both esper abilities and magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.42,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,The result was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.60,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis was my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:53.27,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis was one of the espers brought in by the faction in Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:57.52,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the spells I taught her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:59.23,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis ended up spilling all her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:04.93,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,To save me from the Knights that came to destroy our facility,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:07.91,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis was beaten to death by their maces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.54,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot co-exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:13.62,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Magicians in the world of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.50,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Scientists in the world of science!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:21.17,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't know the boundaries of our own fields properly, the same mistakes will be repeated over and over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:24.45,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, this is not making any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:27.68,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If this is about protecting each other,\Nwhat the hell is starting a war going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.47,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're not actually going to start one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:38.98,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to accomplish what you want,\Nyou just want a situation where they're about to go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.90,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me so highly, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:44.86,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you look at me with pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.03,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,The clay is my ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:52.91,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,And in this abyss surrounded by clay, I am the ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.58,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... she's going to destroy the entire tunnel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.04,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Everything, crumble down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.50,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Like a puppet of mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.96,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, what should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.50,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Touma, did you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:07.65,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The direction and standing position of the caster in the formula used...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:10.54,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Get it wrong just by a little, and it won't function at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.80,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that golden ratio, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:13.81,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.27,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Devour the foolish ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:17.23,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Melt them into the mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:21.19,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The magic seals on the walls and ceiling are used to bury me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:24.15,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,And I will recompose your body with all this mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.57,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, she didn't need to have seals on the ground, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:33.49,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That must mean these seals are the ones that protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:34.91,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.33,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:54.92,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.13,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:04.44,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I need to... create war... the reason for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:08.57,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Academy City is letting down its guard too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:15.28,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Church is letting an outsider have possession of Index Librorum Prohibitorum, showing their naivety.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.80,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same situation that occurred during Ellis' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:21.96,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,A tragedy of that scale took place back then when there were just small factions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:27.31,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,If Academy City and the English Purist Church in their entireties are joining hands-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.55,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.80,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and be angry. Be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:36.15,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But, what the hell did Kazakiri do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.39,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What did Index do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.80,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You point your weapon at someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:43.69,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...and that's when real wars happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.94,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.41,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:50.86,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I want to slaughter all magicians and espers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:53.39,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:57.87,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want magicians and espers fighting each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:03.04,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,My mind was in conflict from the very beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:08.34,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I have more than one conviction...\NI have as many as the number of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:11.53,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:16.18,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that there was only one thing\Nyou believed in from the very beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:22.27,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you just didn't want to lose your dear friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:28.69,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In your eyes, did Index look like she didn't want to be with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:34.11,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Did we look like we were going to fight unless we were isolated in our own separate worlds?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:38.41,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We are able to live together without doing such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:41.79,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So don't take my dear friend away from me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.87,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Intimus115!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:51.76,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:54.72,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When she said she has as many convictions as the number of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:56.93,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Die, esper!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:59.01,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You understood the one emotion inside you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:03.43,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...of wanting someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.02,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...to stop you, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:20.98,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,This may be bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.66,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Long distance manipulation has been switched to automaton mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:24.87,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I can't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.73,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:30.74,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.76,index,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:38.67,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:39.72,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:46.34,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.57,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:14.92,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyou... ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.33,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.45,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.72,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It's still dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:44.01,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The golem went berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.58,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It might be losing control of its regeneration ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.41,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka, let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.73,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,You hurry and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:57.85,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.66,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Hyouka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.43,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I need to stop that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.70,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.68,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You can't think that you can fight a monster like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:10.14,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you'll die for sure, Hyouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.65,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.90,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not human either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:20.03,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... for not telling you all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.11,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:46.76,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,The ones to fight monsters... must also be monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.81,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:53.00,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,That "time" will never happen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:57.82,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.07,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I can't abandon her!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.07,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:07.24,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Because... she's my friend!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.75,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:13.83,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:16.27,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:20.55,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that there's still hope in the world you reside in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.13,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...and that I'd show you that!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.22,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:40.69,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,...and so is the nice illusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.71,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so messy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.68,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:07.93,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me this is your doing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.90,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You know, while this does happen all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.77,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,how much trouble do you have to get yourself into?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:27.91,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.97,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,My, Oneesama!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.24,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,There you are-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.75,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... Oneesama, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:40.49,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:45.31,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,In the very near future,\NJudgment and Anti-Skill will come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:47.91,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Before this gets bad, let's run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.71,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I said this wasn't-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.66,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I knew from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.83,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knew, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:24.46,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,When a monster reveals its true nature, they know what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.30,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:31.18,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,But what could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:33.12,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,A friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:36.95,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,A person who called me a friend for the first time in my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:38.69,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:46.48,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I lose this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:51.83,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I be afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.37,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:14:02.46,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't want my dear friend to get hurt!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.28,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I stood up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:08.86,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be with her forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:12.05,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that I could be good friends with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:16.30,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,But... it was impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:19.72,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,...even if she became scared of me... hated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:23.40,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,...I couldn't watch her get killed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:29.05,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.04,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:39.98,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, then you're not a monster, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:49.24,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I know this sounds corny, but you're human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:50.92,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:53.55,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:56.93,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Your illusion isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.21,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:11.82,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.27,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:21.50,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... not human...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:30.05,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,...yet why is she looking at me... as a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:36.07,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe your composition is a bit different from a human's,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:39.43,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,and you might be able to do things other people can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:41.72,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:52.23,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But, it doesn't change the fact that you're Index's friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:57.57,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,You happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:04.32,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're another step closer to the completion of a key...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.96,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,...that can control the Imaginary Number Sector - Five Elements Institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.84,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, you're a monster to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:15.70,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the Imaginary Number Sector's true nature is the AIM dispersion field itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.84,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure no one would think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:22.52,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, to be adding self-consciousness to and helping the materialization of something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:24.56,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you to be sane at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.44,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, Aleister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.69,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:36.40,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,The Imaginary Number Sector is a kind of aggregation of power that exists in a separate dimension from humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:39.07,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,An organism born from that aggregation is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:43.45,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I know what that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:45.87,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,An angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:51.86,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,If the inhabitants of the Imaginary Number Sector,\Nlike Kazakiri, were "Angels" per se,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:56.01,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,then the city in which they live in would be... in other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:17:00.76,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're trying to artificially create Heaven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:06.02,index,Crowley,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing words like "Angels" and "Heaven" at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.76,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Cut me some slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:09.85,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,As if there'd be someone who'd know more than you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:13.82,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Aleister Crowley, the magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:20.28,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,From this time's incident,\Nthe world has slowly begun to tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:25.66,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,You purposely lured in a member of the English Purist Church and defeated her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:32.05,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,What you're thinking is completely beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:36.55,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're going to take advantage of that Imagine Breaker, then be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:43.10,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Face him with half-assed beliefs,\Nand his right hand will eat your illusions alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:51.98,index,Crowley,0000,0000,0000,,The illusions I believed in... are already in a destroyed state since long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.65,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.79,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'm completely unscratched!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.64,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.90,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is a sign that I'm learning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:04.85,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.19,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:13.67,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,You really, really, really LOVE causing trouble for others, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:18.09,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, for you to be in Anti-Skill's custody...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:23.97,index,Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to be careful of Kazakiri Hyouka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:31.87,index,Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Your personality of going all out when it comes to women needs a good amount of tweaking sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:36.96,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, these two people in the back scare me,\Nso could I stay in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:39.49,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In absolute-rest, no-visitor conditions-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:43.76,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.07,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Your skirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:47.58,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.08,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:52.51,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:54.88,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I really think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.67,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It was already weird to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:00.01,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It might be even weirder now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:01.41,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:07.43,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka, you-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:09.51,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:14.14,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,My body is like a lump of esper power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:21.27,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do, it'll never change the fact that I'm an unstable entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:24.13,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Is this because of Touma's right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:25.11,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:31.81,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,If his powers really affected me,\Nthen I would've been gone already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.34,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:41.27,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,About his power, I don't know too much about it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:45.38,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Esper abilities, alone, aren't enough to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:49.89,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:52.02,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.02,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:01.89,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.92,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry, I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:16.08,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,My body is formed from the powers of many, many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:21.72,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did disappear, it wouldn't mean I'd died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.59,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It'd just mean you wouldn't be able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.88,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:31.38,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I will always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.28,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.90,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hang out together again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:43.91,index,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.91,index,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, second semester is very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:59.79,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,But I have so much time, I'm bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:03.25,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma wouldn't pay attention to me or play with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:08.49,index,blue,0000,0000,0000,,Look, this is what magicians should look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.84,index,blue,0000,0000,0000,,Moe, right? Moe, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:12.65,index,blue,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Hime-yan, you do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:14.54,index,Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... moe then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:18.71,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, boys and girls, we're going to start homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:21.65,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:23.61,index,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Tsuchimikado-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.95,index,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I started my job already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:43.25,index,Yomi,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of those two, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:44.94,index,Yoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:57.97,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:21:59.42,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,My ribbon has drifted into...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.31,index,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,...Oneesama's forbidden sanctuary!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.77,index,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,KUROKO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:23.79,index,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,A situation has arisen where we need\Nthe Index Librorum Prohibitorum's assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:27.23,index,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,Have her keeper come, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:29.20,index,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,"Keeper", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.69,0:22:30.94,index,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:32.84,index,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki and I will leave for Japan right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:36.81,index,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,The problem, however, is we cannot contact Kanzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:40.27,index,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Arc Bishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:44.13,index,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,I am wearing a rather dull attire for a change,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:46.48,index,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,you shan't address me by my formal title.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:49.31,index,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,Laura Stuart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.74,0:22:51.70,index,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,You shall address me by that name.
