Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:05.13,index,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Index-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:10.84,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, you forgot the fridge was empty, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:15.84,index,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, eating something delicious all by yourself...
